    <p>This report explores the key trends and developments that are accelerating the growth of a software-enhanced, networked physical world.  It looks at how networks and data change what's possible with physical devices; how changes in manufacturing and tooling make it possible to bring hardware to market on a shoestring budget; how all companies have to become software companies to remain competitive; and more.</p>                                       
